title: Big Tech’s latest reckoning is coming as it continues to rack up record valuations

title: FAANG Stocks: Ignore These Distractions

title: EU top court to rule in landmark Facebook, Schrems privacy case
text: Europe's top court will on Thursday rule on the legality of tools companies use to transfer Europeans' data around the world, in the latest clash between Facebook and Austrian privacy activist Max Schrems.

title: Belski: MAGA stocks, Facebook were strong before COVID-19 pandemic, will likely remain strong after
